# ===========================================
# NOTES
# ===========================================
# 1. Never commit .env to git (it's in .gitignore)
# 2. For Android Emulator: 10.0.2.2 = your computer's localhost
# 3. For Physical Device: Use your computer's actual IP address
# 4. For Production: Use your deployed server's domain/IP
# 5. After changing .env, restart Metro bundler with: npx react-native start --reset-cache
